<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Support Hotlines</span></h3>
<p><strong>1-800-668-6868</strong><br /><em>This is the Canada Kids Help Line.</em></p>
<p><strong>1-800-399-PEER</strong><br /><em>This is the peer listening line for anyone under 25 years old.</em></p>
<p><strong>1-800-999-9999</strong><br /><em>This line connects the caller to Covenant House NineLine for dealing with a crisis and angry feelings.</em></p>
<p><strong>1-800-784-2433</strong><br /><em>This is the National Hopeline which connects the caller to a 24-hour crisis center near them.</em></p>
